title: Phil McMinn - Director of Digital Marketing

metadata.description: Phil is our Director of Digital Marketing at Torchbox. He works with some of the UK's top charities, NGOs and think tanks, and holds ultimate responsibility for the strategic direction of Torchbox's digital marketing proposition.
